<item>
            <title>[LU-12323] save_stack_trace_tsk is not exported on arm architectures</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12323</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;libcfs module needs save_stack_trace_tsk symbol:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;nm libcfs.ko | grep save_stack_trace_tsk
                 U save_stack_trace_tsk
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Added in 2.12 commit:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;commit afedf9343686504c89f2e28cf6133540166f2347
Author: Yang Sheng &amp;lt;ys@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;
Date:   Wed Aug 8 00:24:19 2018 +0800

    LU-11062 libcfs: use save_stack_trace for stack dump
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, this symbol is not exported on arm architectures:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;*hornc@cflosbld09 sle-cray $ grep save_stack_trace_tsk ./arch/arm{,64}/kernel/stacktrace.c | grep EXPORT
*hornc@cflosbld09 sle-cray $
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the above excerpt I&apos;m checking the SLES 15 4.12.14-25.22 kernel. I&apos;m not yet aware of any other kernels where arm architectures export this symbol.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
